    "description": "Tata Memorial Centre Ventures Solutions is actively seeking a talented and motivated Radiologist to join our dynamic team in Kochi. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Tata Memorial Centre Ventures Solutions:\nTata Memorial Centre Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata Memorial Centre Ventures Solutions!",
